name: Room 702 Shabu Party : Cheese War !
description:
After the long, long week of the final exhibition, one of my classmates from the department of fine arts suggested we go to the international dormitory for shabu. 

Charlotte from room 701 handed a pack of beef. 
Room 706's Sako brings organic eggs. 
Room 703's Lenka presents pork and vegetables. 

There is just one cheese with a smiley face. 
Charlotte and I started a cheese war.
